cations.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9847479572756075, \"rank\": 0.013672514773398876, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The attacks\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"their traditional summer vacations\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crowds were reported in some major stations.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Crowds\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"some major stations\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think of all the French people, all the families, who were preparing to go on vacation,\\\" Prime Minister Attal said.\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2718, \"end\": 2731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the families\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"vacation\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"Prime Minister Attal\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I share their anger and salute their patience, their understanding and the civic-mindedness they demonstrate.\\\"\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their anger\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"their patience\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"their understanding\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"the civic-mindedness\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025Griffin Media.Privacy Policy,